Captain Page Smith, USN;

Mr. John Hancock, Lehmann Brothers, New
                                                  York;

Mr. Frederick Osborn, U.S. Representative on
                                                  the UN Atomic Energy Commission;

Mr. Joseph Volpe, Deputy General Counsel, U.S.
                                                  Atomic Energy Commission;

